  "title": "Gardening Plantation Worker |Horticultural  Gardener",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>5.5 Days Per Week | Sunday OFF</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>8am-5pm (Mon to Fri) | 8am to 12pm (Sat)</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Gardener | Plant Nurturer | Horticultural &amp; Landscape Worker | Plantation Nursery</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic Salary: SGD $1,950 [ Fix ]</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Entitled to Medical Benefits &amp; Bonus</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>This role will work under Landscaping &amp; Plantation Company but outsource to work under various hospitals in Singapore. [ Novena | Jurong East | Sengkang | Yishun | Khatib | Farrer Park | Tengah | Bukit Batok ]</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Must be Covid vaccination certified due to the work environment at hospitals.</li>\n  <li>Prefer those with basic plantation knowledge and gardener experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Scopes:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n  <li>Weeding and mulching landscape beds</li>\n  <li>Trimming small trees, hedges and shrubs</li>\n  <li>Removing unwanted, dead or damaged trees</li>\n  <li>Planting shrubs, flowers and trees</li>\n  <li>Watering gardens, lawns and landscapes</li>\n  <li>Grass cutting</li>\n  <li>Fertilizing plants</li>\n  <li>Monitoring and maintaining plant health</li>\n</ol>\n<p>#SCR-carson-cheong</p>\n<p>⭕ Cheong Kar Chun ⭕ Team Manager ⭕ R1980386</p>\n<p>⭕ The Supreme HR Advisory ⭕ 14C7279</p>",
